Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:09.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}錆び付いていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:11.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}それでも君の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.99,0:01:14.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}言葉も願いも勇気も
