Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:00.90,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}留給這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:03.11,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}時光流逝如梭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.11,0:01:05.48,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}帶走人的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:08.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你刻下的道道軌跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:09.99,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}也漸漸染上鏽斑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:11.99,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}儘管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.99,0:01:14.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你說過的話 你的願望和勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.20,0:01:17.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}現在也毫無疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:19.66,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在我心中迴盪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:21.88,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}踏上同一條旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.88,0:01:23.96,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}明明沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.96,0:01:25.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}卻讓我眼角含淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.59,0:01:30.09,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}不知何時起 我變得想要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.09,0:01:31.30,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}這一切的緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.30,0:01:32.26,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哪怕已經太遲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.26,0:01:34.76,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只要再次踏上與你走過的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:38.18,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哪怕你已經不在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:40.27,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}也一定能夠找到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:51.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}And you alright
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:54.85,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}Can you hear me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:01.65,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}誰もいない線路沿いをなぞってく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:04.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}おおげさに泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:06.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}笑って欲しくて
